						<h1 id="firstHeading">Procedural programming</h1>			
<div class="dablink">This article is about the computer programming paradigm.  For the method of algorithmic content creation, see <a href="http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Procedural_generation" title="Procedural generation">Procedural generation</a>.</div>
